rComments: He is nice, but useless lectures. If you read the textbook there was no reason to go to class, as it was basically a summary. Frankly I read the book and saved myself two hours every Thursday night. Take the course for an easy A. I had an amazing TA though.
Great professor! Made lectures fun and very informative. He answered questions well and went through main-concepts thorughly.

Funny guy, he makes jokes in class and try to be entertaining during the lectures. He goes through important points quickly. Overall, he's a good prof. U need to read to book if u want good marks and that's it!

Awful teacher, touched on key concepts very briefly.  Claimed that he was accessible, but his level of sarcasm and patronization made him unapproachable to many.  He was overall pretty obnoxious and tried infuse too much humor where none was required.
